5b9d6a8add91f8a7a1a26d5","tid":46592,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0571d9945f9122cf7a9fe08282f77dd73e353826","tid":46592,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg&h=7634d9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高汁會然之黑白論述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑白比彩色易咁多適合新手同賴有風格人仕<br />\n1bit更加係燙手可熱既風格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10031971af5dad1a198a1e8dd0d268bfd02e542e","tid":46592,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"講返zone system,其實我覺得啱啱影可以唔理佢住,因為要完全明白同實淺唔容易同埋其實呢個方法已經過時不過都有人歸納出現代版zone system<br />\n無論影彩色又好黑白又好最重要嘅係背後嘅意念,你冇一個好強烈嘅想法就算你執相䁱飛張相出到嚟只有空洞<br />\n其實好多人都覺得影黑白可以突出構圖可以加深層次乜乜乜,不過絕對唔好俾固有嘅想法限制自己,只要你有意念就算你0構圖一樣可以成功<br />\n森山大道就係其中一個例子,佢嘅構圖好除性但係佢好清楚自己想表達啲乜,佢嘅黑白好高對比,但係令到線條更有衝擊<br />\n黑白同彩色相一樣要問自己點解想要呢隻色調,睇番好多大師嘅相例如steve mccurry, eric lafforgue, jimmy nelson,你係睇得出佢地嘅色調係一連串決定嘅成果而唔係一個preset咁簡單,所以你唔應該以某位攝影師為目標因為你係你佢係佢<br />\n其實打咁大篇野就係想講攝影其實冇絕對,亦冇一條成功formula<br />\n藝術唔係好似執藥咁,curry構圖+salagado題材+adams黑白+荒木咸濕=成功<br />\n分析前人嘅作品或者可以歸納出成功要素,但係你只會探索到攝影嘅regression line, outlier 嘅世界你永遠唔會知<br />\n所以我一路都主張不要問只要影,唔須要複習化,你遇到瓶頸就自然會研究相關嘅野,太早睇太多野只會令自迷失,最後可能集百家之大成但係冇自我<br />\n如果你係白紙一張無謂畫花佢<br />\n最後,其實只有一個問題你要問,就係點你要影相,可能到最後發現原來黑白唔係你杯茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4275ac43232e33e77e38397c0fee26c53952d38","tid":46592,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg&h=7634d9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高汁會然之黑白論述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑白比彩色易咁多適合新手同賴有風格人仕<br />\n1bit更加係燙手可熱既風格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsm至係色調皇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝有一日可以成為mccurry junior<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658fc7324957ed39b98950da552d7db008b6b927","tid":46592,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F040347_cad69ccd1fe804110b59ffd70878ae2f.jpg&h=7634d9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高汁會然之黑白論述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑白比彩色易咁多適合新手同賴有風格人仕<br />\n1bit更加係燙手可熱既風格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsm至係色調皇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝有一日可以成為mccurry junior<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD色唔係佢調架佢識撚用電腦咩，識就唔洗比人洗獲金啦<br />\n不過佢D菲林色又係無人扮到, 無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da5c12dade430c151ef8ee2d8cae6091379b0e4","tid":46592,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"一直都想學"},{"pid":"235a363d68e467bf924f58e8a948ff1e00fefcad","tid":46592,"uid":16898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20