00Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講返zone system,其實我覺得啱啱影可以唔理佢住,因為要完全明白同實淺唔容易同埋其實呢個方法已經過時不過都有人歸納出現代版zone system<br />\n無論影彩色又好黑白又好最重要嘅係背後嘅意念,你冇一個好強烈嘅想法就算你執相䁱飛張相出到嚟只有空洞<br />\n其實好多人都覺得影黑白可以突出構圖可以加深層次乜乜乜,不過絕對唔好俾固有嘅想法限制自己,只要你有意念就算你0構圖一樣可以成功<br />\n森山大道就係其中一個例子,佢嘅構圖好除性但係佢好清楚自己想表達啲乜,佢嘅黑白好高對比,但係令到線條更有衝擊<br />\n黑白同彩色相一樣要問自己點解想要呢隻色調,睇番好多大師嘅相例如steve mccurry, eric lafforgue, jimmy nelson,你係睇得出佢地嘅色調係一連串決定嘅成果而唔係一個preset咁簡單,所以你唔應該以某位攝影師為目標因為你係你佢係佢<br />\n其實打咁大篇野就係想講攝影其實冇絕對,亦冇一條成功formula<br />\n藝術唔係好似執藥咁,curry構圖+salagado題材+adams黑白<span style=\"color: red;\">+荒木咸濕=</span>成功<br />\n分析前人嘅作品或者可以歸納出成功要素,但係你只會探索到攝影嘅regression line, outlier 嘅世界你永遠唔會知<br />\n所以我一路都主張不要問只要影,唔須要複習化,你遇到瓶頸就自然會研究相關嘅野,太早睇太多野只會令自迷失,最後可能集百家之大成但係冇自我<br />\n如果你係白紙一張無謂畫花佢<br />\n最後,其實只有一個問題你要問,就係點你要影相,可能到最後發現原來黑白唔係你杯茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n袋sir 下次分段啦，睇得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorly<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5e2378ba9763722ef5dc4b396d13870f07792d","tid":46592,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講返zone system,其實我覺得啱啱影可以唔理佢住,因為要完全明白同實淺唔容易同埋其實呢個方法已經過時不過都有人歸納出現代版zone system<br />\n無論影彩色又好黑白又好最重要嘅係背後嘅意念,你冇一個好強烈嘅想法就算你執相䁱飛張相出到嚟只有空洞<br />\n其實好多人都覺得影黑白可以突出構圖可以加深層次乜乜乜,不過絕對唔好俾固有嘅想法限制自己,只要你有意念就算你0構圖一樣可以成功<br />\n森山大道就係其中一個例子,佢嘅構圖好除性但係佢好清楚自己想表達啲乜,佢嘅黑白好高對比,但係令到線條更有衝擊<br />\n黑白同彩色相一樣要問自己點解想要呢隻色調,睇番好多大師嘅相例如steve mccurry, eric lafforgue, jimmy nelson,你係睇得出佢地嘅色調係一連串決定嘅成果而唔係一個preset咁簡單,所以你唔應該以某位攝影師為目標因為你係你佢係佢<br />\n其實打咁大篇野就係想講攝影其實冇絕對,亦冇一條成功formula<br />\n藝術唔係好似執藥咁,curry構圖+salagado題材+adams黑白<span style=\"color: red;\">+荒木咸濕=</span>成功<br />\n分析前人嘅作品或者可以歸納出成功要素,但係你只會探索到攝影嘅regression line, outlier 嘅世界你永遠唔會知<br />\n所以我一路都主張不要問只要影,唔須要複習化,你遇到瓶頸就自然會研究相關嘅野,太早睇太多野只會令自迷失,最後可能集百家之大成但係冇自我<br />\n如果你係白紙一張無謂畫花佢<br />\n最後,其實只有一個問題你要問,就係點你要影相,可能到最後發現原來黑白唔係你杯茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n袋sir 下次分段啦，睇得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorly<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩，原來大家層次唔同，我只係講緊普通影下相<br />\n原來又表達又藝術又人生意義咁多野, 第日我識用相機希望袋sir教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> zone system 即係乜野?"},{"pid":"d5ca712cca7c9dd98ab05228fae3fece248c2d46","tid":46592,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"樓上某大師話Zone system過時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnsel Adams同森山大道出名影嘜都未分清楚，<br />\n唔好咁井底蛙啦"},{"pid":"188cbe9c516506eec0d5dd06b8d8854aab198ad3","tid":46592,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T20:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上某大師話Zone system過時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnsel Adams同森山大道出名影嘜都未分清楚，<br />\n唔好咁井底蛙啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一 zone system係專係用喺大底負片因為大底可以分開曝光<br />\n第二 zone system原意係喺負片上面保留最多資訊去後製<br />\n第三 大底負片dr同ff cmos dr係兩回事<br />\n第四 數碼相機其實有樣野叫histogram<br />\n<br />\n而且我想講嘅係zone system唔係咩金科玉律,冇必要太早接觸,到樓主摸清想影乜再自然會研究<br />\n你啱啱識揸筆會唔會走去學黃金比列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我全篇野都係講緊攝影心態但係你又可以以為我比較緊佢地嘅style咁撚叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟點先可以完全跳過重點跟住走去屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最搞笑就係其實你咩都冇覆過定係派膠可以論證到我講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8201a34b074547e9e834c9b40297f86572ea9a3","tid":46592,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T23:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n第一 zone system係專係用喺大底負片因為大底可以分開曝光<br />\n第二 zone system原意係喺負片上面保留最多資訊去後製<br />\n第三 大底負片dr同ff cmos dr係兩回事<br />\n第四 數碼相機其實有樣野叫histogram<br />\n<br />\n而且我想講嘅係zone system唔係咩金科玉律,冇必要太早接觸,到樓主摸清想影乜再自然會研究<br />\n你啱啱識揸筆會唔會走去學黃金比列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我全篇野都係講緊攝影心態但係你又可以以為我比較緊佢地嘅style咁撚叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟點先可以完全跳過重點跟住走去屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最搞笑就係其實你咩都冇覆過定係派膠可以論證到我講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一二三四行都解釋唔到點解Zone system過時，<br />\n頭一二三我真係笑左...「專用」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋建議你去磨下書包睇下zone system同histogram嘅關係先再拋書包<br />\n<br />\n一張高質風景相嘅Post提Zone system你就同我講過時，<br />\n我唔屌你屌邊個呀阿叔？<br />\n<br />\n喂，擺到明樓主已經開始揸機，<br />\n佢影D相已經有D sense，<br />\n佢睇多D靚相識多樣嘢有嘜問題？<br />\n你學寫字寫寫下都會去睇下咩叫做寫得靚啦，<br />\n你學睇相都要知張相究竟靚係邊啦<br />\n樓主影影下上黎問點影高質黑白相求進步，<br />\n你話Zone system過時，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔屌你屌邊個呀阿叔？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你覆嘅嘢就永遠藝術藝術掛係嘴邊，<br />\n跳出框框係好事，<br />\n連個框都未知係咩就跳，呢D唔係叫藝術，呢D叫亂黎<br />\n<br />\n新手Po相求評相，<br />\n有心人都要由構圖、曝光呢D基本野開始講起，<br />\n我相信Po果個都係想聽呢類評語。<br />\n唔通個個要係下面淨係留有Feel無Feel呀？<br />\n再者，Zone system係一張有層次黑白相嘅要素，<br />\n我都係要問多句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Zone system過時理據係邊呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋世界上有紀實攝影呢樣嘢，<br />\n唔係下下玩藝術先叫攝影，<br />\n影開相都知，要還原真實先係最難<br />\n<br />\n鳩影我見唔少，大把阿叔影十幾二十年D相都毫無進步，<br />\n同佢講邊度唔好，個個都話自己玩感覺玩藝術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌你就屌你，明屌你講Zone system過時，<br />\n唔洗你Buy我上面講嘅嘢，<br />\n你淨係為講呢句嘅無知Say Sorry先啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">---下面比返樓主睇---</span><br />\n<br />\n如果Ansel Adams你覺得太大佬級，<br />\n下面呢D攝影家都可以比到啟發你<br />\n<br />\nEugene Atget<br />\n（好多舊巴黎相，同埋你發覺佢好多相都係晨早去影，都係層次感嘅一種）<br />\n<br />\nHenri Cartier-Bresson<br />\n（「決定性𣊬間」嘅攝影理念，睇左佢D相就知，好有趣)<br />\n<br />\nRobert Frank<br />\n（「無意識」攝影手法，直接且真實，以影人民為主）<br />\n<br />\nEugene Simth<br />\n（都係影人民為主，我好鐘意嘅一個紀實攝影家，構圖簡單容易令睇相者感受其內容，光線運用亦可以參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"e6a984ad4ff58e7a22381103939a11bc41214114","tid":46592,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一二三四行都解釋唔到點解Zone system過時，<br />\n頭一二三我真係笑左...「專用」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋建議你去磨下書包睇下zone system同histogram嘅關係先再拋書包<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一張高質風景相嘅Post提Zone system你就同我講過時，<br />\n我唔屌你屌邊個呀阿叔？</span><br />\n<br />\n喂，擺到明樓主已經開始揸機，<br />\n佢影D相已經有D sense，<br />\n佢睇多D靚相識多樣嘢有嘜問題？<br />\n你學寫字寫寫下都會去睇下咩叫做寫得靚啦，<br />\n你學睇相都要知張相究竟靚係邊啦<br />\n樓主影影下上黎問點影高質黑白相求進步，<br />\n你話Zone system過時，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔屌你屌邊個呀阿叔？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你覆嘅嘢就永遠藝術藝術掛係嘴邊，<br />\n跳出框框係好事，<br />\n連個框都未知係咩就跳，呢D唔係叫藝術，呢D叫亂黎<br />\n<br />\n新手Po相求評相，<br />\n有心人都要由構圖、曝光呢D基本野開始講起，<br />\n我相信Po果個都係想聽呢類評語。<br />\n唔通個個要係下面淨係留有Feel無Feel呀？<br />\n再者，Zone system係一張有層次黑白相嘅要素，<br />\n我都係要問多句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Zone system過時理據係邊呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋世界上有紀實攝影呢樣嘢，<br />\n唔係下下玩藝術先叫攝影，<br />\n影開相都知，要還原真實先係最難<br />\n<br />\n鳩影我見唔少，大把阿叔影十幾二十年D相都毫無進步，<br />\n同佢講邊度唔好，個個都話自己玩感覺玩藝術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌你就屌你，明屌你講Zone system過時，<br />\n唔洗你Buy我上面講嘅嘢，<br />\n你淨係為講呢句嘅無知Say Sorry先啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">---下面比返樓主睇---</span><br />\n<br />\n如果Ansel Adams你覺得太大佬級，<br />\n下面呢D攝影家都可以比到啟發你<br />\n<br />\nEugene Atget<br />\n（好多舊巴黎相，同埋你發覺佢好多相都係晨早去影，都係層次感嘅一種）<br />\n<br />\nHenri Cartier-Bresson<br />\n（「決定性𣊬間」嘅攝影理念，睇左佢D相就知，好有趣)<br />\n<br />\nRobert Frank<br />\n（「無意識」攝影手法，直接且真實，以影人民為主）<br />\n<br />\nEugene Simth<br />\n（都係影人民為主，我好鐘意嘅一個紀實攝影家，構圖簡單容易令睇相者感受其內容，光線運用亦可以參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nzone system係因為用負片影靜物嘅前期功夫而derive出唻,係一套去量度現場,器材,成品嘅system,係一套pre-visualise嘅system<br />\n<br />\n但係而家所謂嘅zone system只係攞adams把灰度尺用喺後製度,你覺得係咪仲係同一回事?你由到尾一味反駁但係冇建立過論點已經知你有幾熟zone system<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋zone system同matrix其實理論上差唔多<br />\n<br />\n紅字為九唔搭八<br />\n<br />\nzone system絕對唔係入門級嘅理論,實淺都有一定難度,不過可能你未識走已經識流體力學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更何況樓主話啱啱先揸機我只係提議佢冇須要太早接觸混淆自己<br />\n<br />\n咁你係咪覺得用zone system就一定影到靚黑白相?<br />\n<br />\n我冇叫樓主唔好睇相只係冇須要太深究,唔通佢研究bresson就會即刻得到佢嘅攝影眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫樓主跳出框框,而係叫佢唔好set個框框俾自己,不如你講下點解唔可以亂嚟?任何野都係trial and error<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Zone system係一張有層次黑白相嘅要素</span>屌你咁都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再者,高質黑白一定要有層次?<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅藝術係refer緊攝影而唔係fine art photography<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/090353_9f4cd0bc96c09bfb1660968a4cfaa6b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F090353_9f4cd0bc96c09bfb1660968a4cfaa6b7.jpg&h=aa68609d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/090544_d468bffc3058923114242ea4d63ce530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F090544_d468bffc3058923114242ea4d63ce530.jpg&h=d26ae87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ae1x44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAe1x44.jpg&h=c5716505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我影開呢啲洗唔洗同你講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲呀叔影埋啲試機相就係因為佢地好似你咁太執著攝影係啲乜,攝影對你嚟講可能係還原現實但係唔好強加於人ok?<br />\n<br />\nbtw你list嘅攝影師冇用過zone system都一樣活得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗你Buy我上面講嘅嘢，<br />\n你淨係為你嘅無知Say Sorry先啦"},{"pid":"c1b0c91930fb0a81588643a81b3fd4d034a10738","tid":46592,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"新手留名學野"},{"pid":"9cb6d768bf2a7b42062161628dfb6686fc03dbfc","tid":46592,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"[quote］刪成堆廢話[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又擺龍門，又黎此Zone system非彼Zone system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘜都你講晒<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己講完Zone system過時到依家都未認錯，兜咁大個圈做嘜姐？</span></span>"},{"pid":"54384de16cd91fcdf7d5ce320f2932064678248f","tid":46592,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote］刪成堆廢話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又擺龍門，又黎此Zone system非彼Zone system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘜都你講晒<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己講完Zone system過時到依家都未認錯，兜咁大個圈做嘜姐？</span></span>[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我一開波已經講撚左有&quot;現代版&quot;zone system你係咪用屎眼睇野</